@{ ViewBag.Title = "POPIA Act"; }
<div style="max-width:700px;margin:40px auto;padding:24px;font-family:Segoe UI,Arial,sans-serif;">
    <h1>Protection of Personal Information Act (POPIA)</h1>
    <p>SavourSA is committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with South Africa's Protection of Personal Information Act (POPIA), 2013.</p>
    <h3>What we collect</h3>
    <p>We collect your name, email address, phone number, province, and (optionally) a profile picture when you register, solely to provide and personalize the SavourSA service.</p>
    <h3>How we use it</h3>
    <p>Your information is used to manage your account, verify your identity, send you relevant notifications (such as email verification and password reset codes), and — if you opt in — send you recipe tips and newsletter updates.</p>
    <h3>Your rights</h3>
    <p>Under POPIA, you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information at any time. Contact us if you'd like to exercise these rights.</p>
    <a href="/" style="color:#4B5D2A;">← Back to Home</a>
</div>